Package: libnemo-normalize
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Brian West <brian@bkw.org>
Installed-Size: 725
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.34), libfst26 (>= 1.8.4), libgcc-s1 (>= 3.0), libstdc++6 (>= 14), libnemo-normalize-data (= 0.1.0)
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Description: NeMo text normalization via OpenFst - shared library
 A C/C++ shared library wrapping NVIDIA NeMo/OpenFst text normalization
 grammars. Provides a pure C API for text normalization (TN) and inverse
 text normalization (ITN) without requiring Python at runtime.
